				<p>For the past decade, Literary Hub has brought you the best of the book world for free—no paywall. But our future relies on you. In return for a donation, you’ll get <em>an ad-free reading experience</em>, exclusive editors’ picks, book giveaways, and our coveted <em>Joan Didion Lit Hub tote bag</em>. Most importantly, you’ll keep independent book coverage alive and thriving on the internet.</p>
